Enum WeemoCall.CallStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WeemoCall.CallStatus>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<WeemoCall.CallStatus>
    Enclosing interface:
    WeemoCall

    public static enum WeemoCall.CallStatus
extends Enum<WeemoCall.CallStatus>
    Status of a call.
    When asked for it, a call is always created and always have a status. If a call is created to reach an invalid or unavailable userID, it's status is set to ENDED.
